{"tid":196652,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【曾是無綫五美】素顏扮陳松伶家姐 姚瑩瑩走另類路線","createTime":"2017-04-11T12:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T20:58:15.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b60781b013801ef6a15d75e7c98333f25258cdf","tid":196652,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170411/large/1491898284_bfc3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170411%2Flarge%2F1491898284_bfc3.png&h=96957d12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姚瑩瑩在《全職沒女》入面，扮演松松姐姐的家姐羅麗芝，現實中姚瑩瑩細陳松伶一年，不過姚瑩瑩在劇集入面，以素顏示人，而且惡形惡相，加埋含住支牙籤，完全演活一個粗魯大姐，跟《愛．回家》的高貴「樓尚好」扮相大大不同。 <br />\n<br />\n昔日的姚瑩瑩，曾經是不少網民的女神。姚瑩瑩於1991年奪得新加坡環球小姐冠軍，其後代表新加坡參加環球小姐，與袁詠儀參加同一屆環球小姐。之後她來港發展，與曹眾、傅明憲、陳彥行及彭子晴封為「無綫五美」，備受大台力捧。 除住姚瑩瑩生B之後，師奶味濃郁，跟全盛時期的她，身形足足大了一個碼。不過，依家有仔萬事足的瑩瑩，毫不介意。今次在《沒女》更以真面目示人，看來可以殺出一條血路!  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170411/2_499242_0/-%E6%9B%BE%E6%98%AF%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E4%BA%94%E7%BE%8E-%E6%B2%92%E5%A5%B3-%E7%B4%A0%E9%A1%8F%E6%89%AE%E9%99%B3%E6%9D%BE%E4%BC%B6%E5%AE%B6%E5%A7%90-%E5%A7%9A%E7%91%A9%E7%91%A9%E8%B5%B0%E5%8F%A6%E9%A1%9E%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170411%2F2_499242_0%2F-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B6%25AB%25E4%25BA%2594%25E7%25BE%258E-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E5%25A5%25B3-%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E9%25A1%258F%25E6%2589%25AE%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%259D%25BE%25E4%25BC%25B6%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25A7%2590-%25E5%25A7%259A%25E7%2591%25A9%25E7%2591%25A9%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E5%258F%25A6%25E9%25A1%259E%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E7%25B7%259A&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi6zQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e74c4cf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25